A vintage-style illustration of a cyclist viewed from behind, riding along a winding mountain road at golden hour, with a smartphone mounted on the handlebars displaying abstract colorful data visualizations and route maps. The scene features warm sepia and amber tones reminiscent of 1970s travel posters, with rolling hills fading into the misty distance. The cyclist wears classic wool cycling attire, and the composition emphasizes the journey ahead with dramatic perspective lines drawing the eye toward distant peaks. Subtle gear mechanisms and analog gauge elements are artfully integrated into the border corners as decorative motifs, suggesting the blend of traditional cycling with modern technology.
